org.hazelwire.modules
Class Module

java.lang.Object
  org.hazelwire.modules.Module

public class Module
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents a module in the system and is 'linked' with the actual module on the filesystem. This is actually one of the core functionalities of the system and it manages everything that has to do with a particular module.
